    Database entity representing a training document. This is the entity class for the TrainingDocument DTO. This entity contains the following fields:

    • id (database primary key) - an ID unique across all training documents in the database. This ID may change during export and import. Corresponds to TrainingDocument.getId() in DTO.
    • profile - The (master, namespace) tuple the document is associated with. Not mapped in DTO.
    • uri - The uri of the CDocument representing the training document. Corresponds to TrainingDocument.getUri() in DTO.
    • title - The title of the CDocument representing the training document. Corresponds to TrainingDocument.getTitle() in DTO.
    • isAnnotated - Flag indicating whether this document has already been annotated. Corresponds to TrainingDocument.isAnnotated() in DTO.
    • content - The CDocument containing the actual contents of the document. Corresponds to TrainingDocument.getContent() in DTO.
